      "span_text": "MUC1-32mer(-CHGVTSAPDTRPAPGSTAPPAHGVTSAPDTRPA) was synthesized in an automated peptide synthesizer in the Memorial Sloan-Kettering Cancer Center Core Peptide Synthesis Facility, and the Tn-MUC1-32 GalNAc-glycopeptide with 8 mol GalNac incorporated was produced by in vitro glycosylation (see Fig. 1 ) with recombinant human polypeptide GalNAc-transferases T2 and T4 as described previously."
